Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经放学了啊  我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是我在叫春香起床啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这明明应该是春香负责的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就跟平时颠倒过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟平时颠倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  春香  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然醒了就说一声嘛  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要在我身上亲来亲去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你把嘴唇藏起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
