Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  小优
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
