Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到小枫的邮件说是大家来放烟花的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她自己却不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫  琴音没和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她早我两个小时出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像带了很多东西的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来那个包裹里好像有长发的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,长发是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  这是小枫的留言？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了  是不是发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就分成两组去找琴音和小枫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  抽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是试胆大会！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,试胆大会啊  好久没玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊  好可怕啊春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在一起就不会有事的  小优
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吻…吻我一下或许就不会害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优  我也是黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  春香那是橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  怎么看都是黄色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思  我不能和小优在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要相同颜色的组一队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带  我是黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那小雫  我们一组了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这反应是什么情况啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  我是队友你不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小柚感觉完全不会害怕的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事故感不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好可怕～～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  没有感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是优还真是对不住了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那小优  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优她离我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优她离我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优她离我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优她离我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优她离我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优她离我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫  我们一起吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小柚～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,于是进行了交换
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那春香你们10分钟后跟来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优  没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还来得及回头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在耍我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香你也只有现在能说说风凉话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真要有什么情况我可不救你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  我随口说说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十分钟后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尾随而来的美月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优这孩子  居然这么晚还到这种地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  果然和春香同学在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还好平时在头饰上涂了萤光涂料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来这地方还真让人不怎么舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能害怕  想点什么开心的事再尾随吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开心的事…  开心的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月会长  张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能是春香同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会想起春香同学啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…春香  刚刚有没有看到什么东西在闪光？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是我的错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出现啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊  小优
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我扔下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  一下子就传出了悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是…看到了什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟过来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优  你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么东西跟过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  要是跟到这里来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吻…吻我一下或许就不会害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定真会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  小优…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  吻我一下或许就不会害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被看穿了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优  居然这么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要说怪物也是小枫或者琴音的其中一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  春香…快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心中有什么东西觉醒了的春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我平静下来以前  请一直吻着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,停不下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我一定要让你平静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优？优  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在叫我的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  优
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月会长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是跟在你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为什么会抱在一起啊  给我分开！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之姐姐  赶紧从这里出去比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才就在被人喊着名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别吓唬你姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是春香同学一边喊着优的名字一边在接吻吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:19:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有喊名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你整天就这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别走散了  一起行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,注：投怀送抱之后的左拥右抱之姐妹丼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不必了  我就一个人回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟春香同学靠那么近  我的心脏受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕就害怕了  不用不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人在一起就不会害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是这么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就当作是这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.51,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,再注：顺理成章之姐妹丼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
