Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  优  好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,试胆大会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没说是试胆大会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了来放烟花的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还搞抽签什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  似乎多了个不该存在的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是想搞试胆大会的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只准备了烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,试胆大会明年再弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好不容易做了些签
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不抽太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那跟在我后面叫我名字的是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么  别说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就只做了烟花的准备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优  冷静点
